st}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2010}}\n\n{{Oslo Metro}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tjernsrud (Station)}}\n[[Category:Oslo Metro stations in B\u00e6rum]]\n[[Category:Oslo Tramway stations in B\u00e6rum]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 1924]]\n[[Category:Railway stations closed in 2009]]\n[[Category:Disused Oslo Metro stations]]\n[[Category:1924 establishments in Norway]]\n[[Category:2009 disestablishments in Norway]]\n\n{{Oslo-metro-stub}}\n{{Norway-tram-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Rich Farmbrough", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:Update date format tag", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tjernsrud_(station)"}
